        <h1>Department of Information</h1>
        
        <div class="pageDescription"><p>The Department of Information will help to convey the Ministry's political profile, contribute to increased knowledge in society about the culture, media, sports and volunteering policy, communicate the Ministry's key decisions and reviews the current issues and contribute&nbsp;so the intentions of the Freedom of Information Act will be followed up.<br /><br /><strong>Information department's press phone + 47 90 23 10 93 is staffed every weekday between&nbsp;0800 and 1545. Besides this, you may contact the communications director Hanne Gjørtz, tel. 95 75 52 13.</strong></p></div>        
